cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the capacity control of neural networks. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with feed-forward networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IT (Information Theory) as it investigates the capacity of the networks. It could also be categorized under cs.SI (Systems and Control) as it deals with the control of the capacity of the networks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with the capacity and characterization of neural networks.
